# Local dev services (web + voice-server)

When a change affects **`web/voice-server`**, **`web/vite.config.ts`**, or **conversation / WebSocket / proxy** in **`web/src`**, assume the user needs both processes refreshed.

**Do this in the same turn (run the commands yourself):**

1. Free ports **8787** and **5173** (kill listeners if needed).
2. Start **`node server.js`** in `web/voice-server` in the background.
3. Start **`npm run dev`** in `web` in the background.

Then tell the user in one short line that services are up (e.g. localhost:5173 + 8787) and **ask them to test**. Do not leave “请你自行重启” as the only action unless execution failed or permissions blocked you.
